Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天也要精精神神地去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会返还试卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼  肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不休息可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要管我了你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试成绩要给我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天休息考试成绩也不会变  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门喽
