Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:17.35,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,300)}春天的开始、南家的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-93,0:00:-8.-93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还是那么充满人情味的绝妙分数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能不会令春香满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回考试不扭转现状就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  找人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  夏奈不会认真学的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了我这认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  现在没戴眼镜看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪  刚才还戴着的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子没有回应我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  去海边吧去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求别人的时候  比起认真来纯真才更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪  美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高和我家的千秋差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  纯朴的眼神很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然这么说虽然很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成绩不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然也太失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个让你提高成绩的好提议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教美雪功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家教就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好很棒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  这里教我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己稍微动动脑筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  这里教我下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么光偏袒美雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了教美雪的功课才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  不要那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过拜托别人得到想要的只适用于小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量去达成目的这才是学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如夏奈所说的我要靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个气势  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  降了一分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠一个人的力量是不行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不互相帮助是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了夏奈  我第一次得了100分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去做就能成功的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我长高的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以  不过要教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类要互相帮助才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-93,0:00:-8.-93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
